      <title>受欢迎的中国掉期交易降温，表明债券需求下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/popular-china-swap-trade-cools-signaling-lower-demand-for-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一些金融机构已经减少了美元兑换人民币的规模，这表明外国对中国债券的需求可能会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/popular-china-swap-trade-cools-signaling-lower-demand-for-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
